        'markdown' => '<p>﻿Gentis Solutions is seeking a Senior C# / .NET Developer to join our team. This contract-to-hire position is with one of our Fortune 50 clients interested in full-time remote consultants. The ideal candidates will have the required skills listed below and will be eligible and open to being hired by our client at the end of the project\'s duration. This position works alongside an existing team and leverages enterprise-level technologies and processes. If you would like to work at a company that has been recognized for its diversity and inclusion, its work to drive positive social change, and as an environmental leader, make sure you apply below.<br></p>
